    <w:p>
      <w:pPr>
        <w:spacing w:after="160"/>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:ascii="Calibri" w:hAnsi="Calibri"/>
          <w:b w:val="0"/>
          <w:i w:val="0"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>It does not stop at detection. UIAO generates the actual artifacts auditors need—System Security Plans, Plans of Action &amp; Milestones, OSCAL profiles, CycloneDX software bills of materials—all produced automatically from the live state of your environment, signed with cryptographic evidence that proves they have not been tampered with.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
