          <w:sz w:val="22"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Think of it this way: UIAO replaces the binder with a living system. Your compliance posture is not a document you update once a year. It is a measurement you can read at any moment.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
